      "snippet": "In the 3rd NBA Summer League game, Portland Trail Blazers defeated New Orleans Pelicans 93–87. Yang Hansen recorded 15 points (6 in 13), 3 rebounds, 2 assists, 1 steal, and 2 blocks within 26 minutes, setting a personal Summer League career high in scoring.</p>",
